<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043751>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Six morphometric characters (expressed in % SL) plotted against SL for Parupeneus jansenii from three different areas." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1043751/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043757>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Four meristic characters for Parupeneus jansenii and P. heptacanthus, with results of statistical interspecific comparisons indicating significant differences based on χ 2 test for trends (upper three charts) or Fisher’s exact test for 2 x 2 tables (lowermost chart)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1043757/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

